name: Flashback April fools day logo
description:
Replaces the original Flashback logo with special Lunarstorm theme ("April 2010 #2") and keeps bjarne-cat intact. Made by deodorant@flashback.org.

This script does not remove ads though, you should support flashback!
But, since there's a lot of other ways to remove these ads, you can fix that problem by yourself.
